##100 kilometers away from Wuhan Tianmen, where the epidemic is even more heart-wrenching!

Micro Signal RSZMDFJ

Function introduction, human is the scale of all things, human is the most beautiful scenery.

Editor's Note:

The following article is from Yuelushan, the author of Yuelushan

Yue Road, Yue road, Yue Lu Shan.

Photo and caption by Lu Shan

February 4,2020

Start of spring

Day 13 of the siege of Wuhan

The 12th day of the closing of the gate of Heaven

1. Confirmed diagnosis

One morning, when the door was opened and the sun was shining all over the toy stethoscope on the bench, it was recorded. The News of the epidemic was so overwhelming that even the three-year-old children seemed to understand it, checking their families daily with a toy stethoscope.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The outbreak of the new coronavirus was in Wuhan, and the city with the highest mortality rate was Tianmen. As of 1500 hours on February 4,117 new coronavirus cases had been confirmed in Tianmen, 10 had died and 0 had been cured, with a mortality rate of 8.5% . As Hubei's most inconspicuous city, poor medical conditions, low attention, I hope the government and the media in Wuhan, Huanggang and other cities in the case of the epidemic, also pay attention to this my beloved home.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
2. Empty City

Yes, I came back from Wuhan, also the day before the city was closed, but to escape this blame, we do not bear, at least most people can not bear. Because, before we shut down the city, we knew what the government wanted us to know.

Before that, the government had not issued any document to explain the severity of the epidemic, and even a few days ago, on a normal working day in Wuhan, the subway, shopping malls and other places, less than a quarter of the number of people wearing masks. Originally with friends about the Spring Festival travel is also all gone, returned all the train tickets and hotel reservations, will be isolated at home.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
3. Village Road

The village road can barely miss traffic, in the past Spring Festival, the traffic jam rate is not lower than the first-tier cities, so we often joked that the village entrance to build a fee-paying parking lot... and now, after the road closure, in addition to the daily epidemic radio car through, the quiet is terrible!

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
4. Take care of

The outbreak is developing rapidly and getting worse, and masks are hard to come by. I used the half-bag of face masks I hadn't used when I was working in Beijing the year before last. During the period, many friends to send me masks and supplies, the province is closed, not to mention express delivery, has been stopped... here, thank you for your concern.

I hope you try not to go out, to protect themselves, is to protect the world!

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
5. Surplus food

This picture is the surplus grain of years ago, has passed nearly half a month now. We don't know when the outbreak will go away, and we don't know how much food we have in the house. The countryside is not like the city, the city also has the government to arrange the distribution, or orders by oneself. In rural areas, after the road closure, only the "food storage" , Three Meals a Day changed to two meals a day, meat dishes are also reduced..

How long can you last with what's left in your house?

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
6. Quarantined

The village a row of houses, a total of 10 families, including seven families from Wuhan back, including me. Because all are self-driving, did not take any public transport, back to the village after the basic self-isolation, all have passed the incubation period. But almost no one wear masks, not do not want to wear, is simply not available, pharmacies closed, express delivery stopped, road closures... It seems that all can only rely on luck!

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
7. Entertainment

It's been two weeks since my return, and although the adults live in daily fear of the epidemic, they still need to have some fun for the children. From our childhood hopscotch, fireworks, jump to pile blocks, read picture books, get up early to take the children to the fields to meet dew, homemade handicrafts... some people joked that, under the epidemic, "forced" became a good father.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
8. Share

The child disposition is particularly cheerful, has what to eat to play always likes with other children to share together. I often want to go back to the outdoor time in Wuhan, with her good friends... but the epidemic is getting worse, I can't go anywhere, sometimes I can only play on the roof..

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
9. Company

If you can't go out, spend time at home with your family, with your kids. The busy work in the past, let me to accompany the day of special treasure, a chance will take the family to share the beautiful time outdoors. And right now, being safe together is the best company.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
10. Colorful

Childhood is supposed to be colorful. I hope that this innocent smile can be more blooming in the blue sky, not be covered by this mask.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
11. Come on

In the roof accidentally see, tile roof red tile was"+"and"U", they took down. Almost all people are refueling in Wuhan, here I want to refuel Tianmen, hope that media attention Tianmen, can have medical supplies delivered to help Tianmen, tide over the difficulties.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
12. Victory

I believe that the Bright Sun will eventually light up the land, the cherry blossoms will bloom again, the premature people will still eat hot dry noodles, the streets will be noisy again, we will take off the mask, to go to their own place, to see the people.

For this, we refuel together!

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Every infectious disease is a disaster for all of mankind. Some people pay for it with tears, sweat and even life. Hubei people have blamed themselves, angry, grateful, red neck, red eye socket, but all the time, our common enemy is only a Florida virus.

Through the test of life and death, I wish you and I can safely spend together!
